        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nおはようございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nGood morning‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すまない、随分待たせてしまった\n今日から新メンバーに合流してもらうことになったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to keep you waiting.\nToday’s the day you meet the new members of your team.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "本当？\nよかったぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?\nWhat a relief…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに心配だったのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was it worrying you that much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "だって、みんなに嫌だって言われたら\nずっと一人になっちゃうかもしれなかったんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yeah. If nobody wanted to team up with me‚\nI would’ve been on my own forever‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.23287787884474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（一人で淋しくても、平気を装って練習を）\n（続けてきたさくらに、俺は申し訳ない気持ちになった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I feel a wave of guilt at the thought of Sakura practicing alone‚）\n（pretending to be unconcerned despite her loneliness.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.377777767181385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、早速入ってもらうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ let’s not waste any time. Come in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.511111100514725,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2466.6666666666615,
          "startTime": 39.97777776718139
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3166.6666666666642,
          "startTime": 40.67777776718139
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "あの……千……です………………\nよ、よろしく……します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ hi… I’m… Chi…\nN-nice to… meet you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.44444443384805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……悪いけど、もう少し\n大きな声でお願い出来るかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sorry‚\nbut could you repeat that a bit louder?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.94814062118528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　あ……すみません\n白石……千紗です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?! Oh‚ uh… sorry.\nI’m… Chisa Shiraishi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.34814062118528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "よろしく……お願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to… meet you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.77480719884234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "白石？\nもしかして、沙季さんの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shiraishi?\nWait‚ are you Saki-san’s…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.14147391319273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "……はい…………妹です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… I’m her little sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.40814057985938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり！\n目の所とか似てる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That explains it!\nYou have the same eyes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.96761895815528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか……\nお姉ちゃんとは全然違うと思うけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "D-do we?\nI feel like I’m her complete opposite….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.83428562482196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、お姉ちゃんと別々のグループでいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You sure you’re okay not being in the same group as her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.86761895815529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "一緒がいいけど、応募した時\nお姉ちゃんは合格して、私は落ちちゃったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d rather be with her‚ but when I auditioned‚\nmy sister made it in‚ and I didn’t.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.06460297902422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（そう、最初の募集の時に）\n（姉の沙季は合格して、妹の千紗は不合格だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That’s right. At the first auditions‚）\n（her sister passed‚ but she failed.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（しかしグループは別でも、姉の近くで）\n（一緒に頑張れるなら……と言ってくれた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Yet she still agreed to join this group.）\n（She said she was happy just to be near her sister.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8358499526977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 110.14018100102732
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_04-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……\nじゃあ、お姉ちゃんと一緒に頑張ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nAlright‚ let's work hard together with your sister!",
        "id": ""
