      "text": "（千紗は自然と雫のスマホを覗き込む体勢になる）\n（そこには麻奈のライブ映像が映っていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Chisa leans in and peeks at Shizuku’s phone.）\n（She is watching one of Mana’s lives.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.29287921587604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
